➜合肥市第八水厂投产并网
http://www.sohu.com/a/428713844_114731	2461
<p>原标题：八水厂来了 </p>
<p align="center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201101/631f3371d0cc49498598c343a957eeda.jpeg" /></p>
